41
0:01:52.26,000 --> 0:01:55,000
These places, these origins,

42
0:01:55.26,000 --> 0:01:57,000
represent governance gaps.

43
0:01:57.26,000 --> 0:01:59,000
That's the politest description

44
0:01:59.26,000 --> 0:02:02,000
I have for them.

