0:02:02.26,000 --> 0:02:04,000
These are the dark pools

46
0:02:04.26,000 --> 0:02:07,000
where global supply chains begin --

47
0:02:07.26,000 --> 0:02:09,000
the global supply chains,

48
0:02:09.26,000 --> 0:02:12,000
which bring us our favorite brand name products.

49
0:02:12.26,000 --> 0:02:15,000
Some of these governance gaps

50
0:02:15.26,000 --> 0:02:18,000
are run by rogue states.

51
0:02:18.26,000 --> 0:02:2,000
Some of them are not states anymore at all.

52
0:02:20.26,000 --> 0:02:22,000
They're failed states.

53
0:02:22.26,000 --> 0:02:24,000
Some of them

54
0:02:24.26,000 --> 0:02:27,000
